column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.mode, p.petroRad_u, p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z, p.deVRad_u, p.deVRad_g, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRad_i, p.deVRad_z, p.deVAB_u, p.deVAB_g, p.deVAB_r, p.deVAB_i, p.deVAB_z, p.deVPhi_u, p.deVPhi_g, p.deVPhi_r, p.deVPhi_i, p.deVPhi_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoPrimary p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
